queries.sql: SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`icon` FROM `product_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb2`.`module` = 'product_catalogue' AND `tb2`.`objectid` = `tb1`.`id` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`lft` > '2' AND `tb1`.`rgt` < '17' ORDER BY `tb1`.`order` desc, `tb1`.`parentid` asc, `tb2`.`title` asc LIMIT 200

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`viewed`, `tb1`.`hot`, `tb1`.`created_at`, `tb1`.`productid`, `tb1`.`bar_code`, `tb1`.`model`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`price`, `tb1`.`rate`, `tb1`.`price_promotion`, `tb1`.`album`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`meta_title`, `tb3`.`meta_description`, `tb3`.`module`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb1`.`model`, `tb1`.`bar_code`, `tb3`.`info`, `tb1`.`length`, `tb1`.`width`, `tb4`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb4`.`canonical` as `cat_canonical` FROM `product` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `object_relationship` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = 'product' INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "product" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb4` ON `tb1`.`catalogueid` = `tb4`.`objectid` AND `tb4`.`module` = "product_catalogue" AND `tb4`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb2`.`catalogueid` IN ('3','9','12','13','14','15','16','18','20','21','22','23','24') GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`order` desc, `tb1`.`id` desc LIMIT 20

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb1`.`image` FROM `product_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb2`.`objectid` = `tb1`.`id` WHERE `tb1`.`lft` > '2' AND `tb1`.`rgt` < '17' AND `tb1`.`level` = 3 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb2`.`module` = 'product_catalogue' ORDER BY `order` desc, `id` desc

SELECT `tb4`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`alt`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb2`.`description` as `cat_description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb4`.`image` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`catalogueid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "slide" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`keyword` = 'slide-banner' GROUP BY `tb4`.`id`

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc

SELECT `tb2`.`title`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb1`.`price`, `tb1`.`price_promotion`, `tb1`.`model`, `tb1`.`bar_code`, `tb2`.`made_in` FROM `product` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb2`.`module` = "product" AND `tb2`.`objectid` = `tb1`.`id` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`hot` = 1 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`created_at` desc LIMIT 5

SELECT `tb2`.`title`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`description`, `tb1`.`created_at` FROM `article` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `article_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb2`.`module` = "article" AND `tb2`.`objectid` = `tb1`.`id` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`hot` = 1 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`created_at` desc LIMIT 5

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc

SELECT `tb4`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`alt`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb2`.`description` as `cat_description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb4`.`image` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`catalogueid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "slide" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`keyword` = 'customer' GROUP BY `tb4`.`id`

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc
